Description: Brand new with tags, authentic Vera Bradley Travel Duffel Bag in the Cha-Cha with Black pattern from the Streeterville collection. This carry-on compliant bag is made from a poly twill fabrication featuring a water-repellent finish and black leather trim. The exterior features a front zip pocket and a trolly sleeve on the back. Inside the Travel Duffel Bag are a slip pocket and a zipper pocket. The Travel Duffel Bag closes with a gold toned zipper. Manufacturer Care Tips state to Hand wash cold, only non-chlorine bleach if needed; lay flat to dry. For MOST, this bag is plenty large enough for at least 3 days worth of clothing, shoes and toiletries and for some it maybe even more like 4-5 days! Retail price on this spacious bag is $238. The Travel Duffel Bag is a large bag, measuring 20" w x 14" h x 9" d with 6 ½" strap drop; 48 ½" removable, adjustable strap. All items come from a smoke free, pet free home.
